Class Director

java.lang.Object
Director
public class Director extends Object
Director is the class which contains all the values for the columns of the Directors table It also contains extra values for the intermediate tables that link the many-to-many relationships, which in this case is the awardWinningDirector table. These values are retrieved through a series of methods in the Parsers Class, and they are also inputted to the actual database using methods in the PopulateDB class
